{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":999,"text":"A year ago, we were invited\nby the Swiss Embassy in Berlin"},{"time":4365,"text":"to present our art projects."},{"time":6999,"text":"We are used to invitations,\nbut this invitation really thrilled us."},{"time":11586,"text":"The Swiss Embassy in Berlin is special."},{"time":14451,"text":"It is the only old building\nin the government district"},{"time":17443,"text":"that was not destroyed\nduring the Second World War,"},{"time":20423,"text":"and it sits right next\nto the Federal Chancellery."},{"time":23723,"text":"No one is closer to Chancellor Merkel\nthan the Swiss diplomats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27863,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30656,"text":"The government district in Berlin\nalso contains the Reichstag --"},{"time":34499,"text":"Germany's parliament --\nand the Brandenburg Gate,"},{"time":37334,"text":"and right next to the gate\nthere are other embassies,"},{"time":40299,"text":"in particular the US\nand the British Embassy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44657,"text":"Although Germany is an advanced democracy,"},{"time":47897,"text":"citizens are limited\nin their constitutional rights"},{"time":50882,"text":"in its government district."},{"time":52299,"text":"The right of assembly and the right\nto demonstrate are restricted there."},{"time":57607,"text":"And this is interesting\nfrom an artistic point of view."},{"time":61299,"text":"The opportunities to exercise\nparticipation and to express oneself"},{"time":66035,"text":"are always bound to a certain order"},{"time":68299,"text":"and always subject\nto a specific regulation."},{"time":71798,"text":"With an awareness of the dependencies\nof these regulations,"},{"time":76581,"text":"we can gain a new perspective."},{"time":79299,"text":"The given terms and conditions\nshape our perception, our actions"},{"time":83977,"text":"and our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86168,"text":"And this is crucial in another context."},{"time":89299,"text":"Over the last couple of years,"},{"time":90801,"text":"we learned that from the roofs\nof the US and the British Embassy,"},{"time":95299,"text":"the secret services have been listening\nto the entire district,"},{"time":100060,"text":"including the mobile phone\nof Angela Merkel."},{"time":103299,"text":"The antennas of the British GCHQ are\nhidden in a white cylindrical radome,"},{"time":108299,"text":"while the listening post\nof the American NSA"},{"time":111340,"text":"is covered by radio transparent screens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115342,"text":"But how to address these hidden\nand disguised forces?"},{"time":118903,"text":"With my colleague, Christoph Wachter,"},{"time":121299,"text":"we accepted the invitation\nof the Swiss Embassy."},{"time":124783,"text":"And we used this opportunity\nto exploit the specific situation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130508,"text":"If people are spying on us,\nit stands to reason"},{"time":133674,"text":"that they have to listen\nto what we are saying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136299,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":140299,"text":"On the roof of the Swiss Embassy,\nwe installed a series of antennas."},{"time":146729,"text":"They weren't as sophisticated as those\nused by the Americans and the British."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151007,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":152298,"text":"They were makeshift can antennas,"},{"time":154045,"text":"not camouflaged but totally\nobvious and visible."},{"time":158299,"text":"The Academy of Arts joined the project,"},{"time":160818,"text":"and so we built another\nlarge antenna on their rooftop,"},{"time":164532,"text":"exactly between the listening posts\nof the NSA and the GCHQ."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168574,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":170454,"text":"Never have we been observed in such detail\nwhile building an art installation."},{"time":175299,"text":"A helicopter circled over our heads"},{"time":177575,"text":"with a camera registering\neach and every move we made,"},{"time":180829,"text":"and on the roof of the US Embassy,\nsecurity officers patrolled."},{"time":185499,"text":"Although the government district\nis governed by a strict police order,"},{"time":190712,"text":"there are no specific laws\nrelating to digital communication."},{"time":195548,"text":"Our installation\nwas therefore perfectly legal,"},{"time":199055,"text":"and the Swiss Ambassador\ninformed Chancellor Merkel about it."},{"time":203101,"text":"We named the project \"Can You Hear Me?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":206004,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":208805,"text":"The antennas created an open\nand free Wi-Fi communication network"},{"time":213090,"text":"in which anyone who wanted to\nwould be able to participate"},{"time":216299,"text":"using any Wi-Fi-enabled device\nwithout any hindrance,"},{"time":219435,"text":"and be able to send messages"},{"time":221380,"text":"to those listening on the frequencies\nthat were being intercepted."},{"time":226510,"text":"Text messages, voice chat, file sharing --"},{"time":229029,"text":"anything could be sent anonymously."},{"time":232852,"text":"And people did communicate."},{"time":235299,"text":"Over 15,000 messages were sent."},{"time":238299,"text":"Here are some examples."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241299,"text":"\"Hello world, hello Berlin,\nhello NSA, hello GCHQ.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":247208,"text":"\"NSA Agents, Do the Right Thing!\nBlow the whistle!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":252884,"text":"\"This is the NSA. In God we trust.\nAll others we track!!!!!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":256612,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":260233,"text":"\"#@nonymous is watching #NSA #GCHQ -\nwe are part of your organizations."},{"time":264299,"text":"# expect us. We will #shutdown\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":267483,"text":"\"This is the NSA's Achilles heel.\nOpen Networks.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":270967,"text":"\"Agents, what twisted story of yourself\nwill you tell your grandchildren?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":276454,"text":"\"@NSA My neighbors are noisy.\nPlease send a drone strike.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":280894,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":284529,"text":"\"Make Love, Not cyberwar.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":287602,"text":"We invited the embassies\nand the government departments"},{"time":290299,"text":"to participate in the open network, too,"},{"time":293129,"text":"and to our surprise, they did."},{"time":295066,"text":"Files appeared on the network,\nincluding classified documents"},{"time":298010,"text":"leaked from the parliamentary\ninvestigation commission,"},{"time":300652,"text":"which highlights that the free exchange\nand discussion of vital information"},{"time":304366,"text":"is starting to become difficult,\neven for members of a parliament."},{"time":309746,"text":"We also organized guided tours\nto experience and sound out"},{"time":313092,"text":"the power constellations on-site."},{"time":315166,"text":"The tours visited the restricted zones\naround the embassies,"},{"time":318527,"text":"and we discussed the potential\nand the highlights of communication."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324299,"text":"If we become aware of the constellation,"},{"time":328502,"text":"the terms and conditions of communication,"},{"time":331322,"text":"it not only broadens our horizon,"},{"time":333677,"text":"it allows us to look behind\nthe regulations that limit our worldview,"},{"time":337573,"text":"our specific social, political\nor aesthetic conventions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":342461,"text":"Let's look at an actual example."},{"time":345383,"text":"The fate of people living\nin the makeshift settlements"},{"time":348494,"text":"on the outskirts of Paris"},{"time":350245,"text":"is hidden and faded from view."},{"time":353299,"text":"It's a vicious circle."},{"time":355299,"text":"It's not poverty, not racism,\nnot exclusion that are new."},{"time":358575,"text":"What is new is how\nthese realities are hidden"},{"time":362117,"text":"and how people are made invisible"},{"time":363769,"text":"in an age of global and overwhelming\ncommunication and exchange."},{"time":368595,"text":"Such makeshift settlements\nare considered illegal,"},{"time":371454,"text":"and therefore those living in them\ndon't have a chance"},{"time":374750,"text":"of making their voices heard."},{"time":376575,"text":"On the contrary, every time they appear,\nevery time they risk becoming visible,"},{"time":382025,"text":"merely gives grounds\nfor further persecution,"},{"time":384759,"text":"expulsion and suppression."},{"time":386792,"text":"What interested us was how we could\ncome to know this hidden side."},{"time":392020,"text":"We were searching for an interface\nand we found one."},{"time":395433,"text":"It's not a digital interface,\nbut a physical one: it's a hotel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399720,"text":"We named the project \"Hotel Gelem.\""},{"time":402783,"text":"Together with Roma families,\nwe created several Hotel Gelems in Europe,"},{"time":406640,"text":"for example, in Freiburg in Germany,\nin Montreuil near Paris,"},{"time":409623,"text":"and also in the Balkans."},{"time":411299,"text":"These are real hotels."},{"time":412684,"text":"People can stay there."},{"time":414299,"text":"But they aren't a commercial enterprise."},{"time":416299,"text":"They are a symbol."},{"time":418575,"text":"You can go online and ask\nfor a personal invitation"},{"time":422251,"text":"to come and live for a few days\nin the Hotel Gelem, in their homes,"},{"time":426661,"text":"eating, working and living\nwith the Roma families."},{"time":430748,"text":"Here, the Roma families\nare not the travelers;"},{"time":433939,"text":"the visitors are."},{"time":435584,"text":"Here, the Roma families\nare not a minority;"},{"time":438663,"text":"the visitors are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441833,"text":"The point is not to make judgments,"},{"time":445826,"text":"but rather to find out\nabout the context that determines"},{"time":448604,"text":"these disparate and seemingly\ninsurmountable contradictions."},{"time":452299,"text":"In the world of globalization,"},{"time":454563,"text":"the continents are drifting\ncloser to each other."},{"time":457299,"text":"Cultures, goods and people\nare in permanent exchange,"},{"time":459847,"text":"but at the same time, the gap\nbetween the world of the privileged"},{"time":463125,"text":"and the world of the excluded is growing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467591,"text":"We were recently in Australia."},{"time":469299,"text":"For us, it was no problem\nto enter the country."},{"time":471924,"text":"We have European passports,\nvisas and air tickets."},{"time":475059,"text":"But asylum seekers who arrive\nby boat in Australia"},{"time":478785,"text":"are deported or taken to prison."},{"time":481299,"text":"The interception of the boats"},{"time":482798,"text":"and the disappearance of the people\ninto the detention system"},{"time":485903,"text":"are veiled by the Australian authorities."},{"time":489062,"text":"These procedures are declared\nto be secret military operations."},{"time":493768,"text":"After dramatic escapes\nfrom crisis zones and war zones,"},{"time":496936,"text":"men, women and children\nare detained by Australia without trial,"},{"time":501071,"text":"sometimes for years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505036,"text":"During our stay, however,"},{"time":507156,"text":"we managed to reach out and work\nwith asylum seekers who were imprisoned,"},{"time":511299,"text":"despite strict screening and isolation."},{"time":514057,"text":"From these contexts was born\nan installation in the art space"},{"time":518190,"text":"of the Queensland University\nof Technology in Brisbane."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522635,"text":"On the face of it,\nit was a very simple installation."},{"time":526182,"text":"On the floor, a stylized compass\ngave the direction"},{"time":529611,"text":"to each immigration detention center,"},{"time":531643,"text":"accompanied by the distance\nand the name of the immigration facility."},{"time":536299,"text":"But the exhibition step\ncame in the form of connectivity."},{"time":540642,"text":"Above every floor marking,\nthere was a headset."},{"time":544299,"text":"Visitors were offered the opportunity\nto talk directly to a refugee"},{"time":548939,"text":"who was or had been imprisoned"},{"time":551299,"text":"in a specific detention facility"},{"time":553511,"text":"and engage in a personal conversation."},{"time":556916,"text":"In the protected context\nof the art exhibition,"},{"time":559806,"text":"asylum seekers felt free\nto talk about themselves,"},{"time":562457,"text":"their story and their situation,\nwithout fear of consequences."},{"time":566694,"text":"Visitors immersed themselves\nin long conversations"},{"time":569730,"text":"about families torn apart,\nabout dramatic escapes from war zones,"},{"time":573507,"text":"about suicide attempts,"},{"time":575143,"text":"about the fate of children in detention."},{"time":578618,"text":"Emotions ran deep. Many wept."},{"time":580626,"text":"Several revisited the exhibition."},{"time":583032,"text":"It was a powerful experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586459,"text":"Europe is now facing a stream of migrants."},{"time":591413,"text":"The situation for the asylum seekers\nis made worse by contradictory policies"},{"time":595299,"text":"and the temptation\nof militarized responses."},{"time":599299,"text":"We have also established\ncommunication systems"},{"time":602013,"text":"in remote refugee centers\nin Switzerland and Greece."},{"time":605622,"text":"They are all about providing\nbasic information -- weather forecasts,"},{"time":608877,"text":"legal information, guidance."},{"time":611163,"text":"But they are significant."},{"time":613211,"text":"Information on the Internet"},{"time":614553,"text":"that could ensure survival\nalong dangerous routes"},{"time":617307,"text":"is being censored,"},{"time":618724,"text":"and the provision of such information\nis becoming increasingly criminalized."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624601,"text":"This brings us back to our network\nand to the antennas"},{"time":627675,"text":"on the roof of the Swiss Embassy in Berlin"},{"time":629929,"text":"and the \"Can You Hear Me?\" project."},{"time":632725,"text":"We should not take it for granted\nto be boundlessly connected."},{"time":635959,"text":"We should start making\nour own connections,"},{"time":638016,"text":"fighting for this idea of an equal\nand globally interconnected world."},{"time":642540,"text":"This is essential to overcome\nour speechlessness"},{"time":645299,"text":"and the separation provoked\nby rival political forces."},{"time":648839,"text":"It is only in truly exposing ourselves"},{"time":652054,"text":"to the transformative power\nof this experience"},{"time":654944,"text":"that we can overcome\nprejudice and exclusion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658299,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659477,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":664835,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Thank you, Mathias."},{"time":666546,"text":"The other half of your\nartistic duo is also here."},{"time":668895,"text":"Christoph Wachter, come onstage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670556,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":675938,"text":"First, tell me just a detail:"},{"time":677367,"text":"the name of the hotel\nis not a random name."},{"time":679470,"text":"Gelem means something specific\nin the Roma language."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682755,"text":"Mathias Jud: Yes, \"Gelem, Gelem\"\nis the title of the Romani hymn,"},{"time":687597,"text":"the official, and it means\n\"I went a long way.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":690980,"text":"BG: That's just to add\nthe detail to your talk."},{"time":693223,"text":"But you two traveled\nto the island of Lesbos"},{"time":695931,"text":"very recently, you're just back\na couple of days ago,"},{"time":698646,"text":"in Greece, where thousands\nof refugees are arriving"},{"time":701078,"text":"and have been arriving\nover the last few months."},{"time":703390,"text":"What did you see there\nand what did you do there?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":705856,"text":"Christoph Wachter: Well, Lesbos is one\nof the Greek islands close to Turkey,"},{"time":709681,"text":"and during our stay,"},{"time":711100,"text":"many asylum seekers arrived by boat\non overcrowded dinghies,"},{"time":716545,"text":"and after landing, they were left\ncompletely on their own."},{"time":720228,"text":"They are denied many services."},{"time":724043,"text":"For example, they are not allowed\nto buy a bus ticket"},{"time":726561,"text":"or to rent a hotel room,"},{"time":727990,"text":"so many families literally\nsleep in the streets."},{"time":732700,"text":"And we installed networks there\nto allow basic communication,"},{"time":737360,"text":"because I think, I believe,"},{"time":739487,"text":"it's not only that we have to speak\nabout the refugees,"},{"time":744950,"text":"I think we need to start talking to them."},{"time":748655,"text":"And by doing so, we can realize\nthat it is about human beings,"},{"time":752299,"text":"about their lives\nand their struggle to survive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":755086,"text":"BG: And allow them to talk as well."},{"time":757020,"text":"Christoph, thank you for coming to TED."},{"time":758959,"text":"Mathias, thank you for coming to TED\nand sharing your story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762001,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}